Pending

Minute or less

Wait for Locks

Minutes

Prepare Task

Minute or less

Marking LDR Decommissioned

Minutes

Decommissioning Replicated and Erasure-Coded Data

Hours, days, or weeks based on the amount of data

Note: If you need to perform other maintenance activities, you can pause the site decommission during this stage. LDR Set State

